title: Vacant-HI2U
description:
Vacant (c) H L Nunnelly

Release 20th August, 2017

Protection: Steam
Game Size: 1 DISC

Game Type: Adventure, Casual, Indie [RELEASE NOTES]

Vacant is a point and click science fiction adventure game about Jade
Bridgett-- a new intern at a mysterious government agency called "The Eye"
On her first day, she gets put on a case to find three missing people
all at which are presumed dead. It's your job to find them and the culprit 

[INSTALL NOTES] 

1 Unpack 2 Mount / burn image 3 Install 4 Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files 5 Play game
